snippet.title: Tere Bin Ep 05 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Nisa BB Cream - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 05 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Nisa BB Cream - 11th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally presented by Nisa BB Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma
Sohail Sameer as Anwar
Sabeena Farooq as Haya
Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra
Mahmood Aslam as Malik Mukhtaar
Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3666 - 12 Jan 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3666: Party Sharty Ka Nateeja
--------------------------------------------------------
Even though Bagha is taken to society by all the Gokuldham men, his peculiar conduct persists because of his intoxication. Bagha declines to take the medications when Dr. Hathi brings them out of his office. In an effort to get Bagha to agree to take the medication, Bhide amuses him by making amusing impersonations. Bagha warns everyone that if he is made to take the pills, he will depart in Sodhi's jeep. Bagha refuses to take the tablets. Alarmed, the women of Gokuldham descend to look about. Bagha ascends the balcony and moves closer to the edge. Everyone is concerned that he might lose his balance. Stay tuned!

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3666, 12 Jan 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000204229

snippet.description:

#AHIMSA  #AHIMSATrailer  #Teja #RPPatnaik #Kiran #Geethika #RajatBedi #Sada  

Director Teja, Anandi Arts Creations‚Äô AHIMSA Shoot Wrapped Up

Director Teja has the calibre to deliver blockbusters with stars as well as upcoming actors. He indeed introduced many actors with his films and some of them become stars. He has proved numerous times that content is the king and films with good content do wonders at box office.

Teja is now introducing another debutant Abhiram as a hero with a youthful entertainer Ahimsa. This is going to be perfect Teja mark movie with the story incorporated with all the commercial ingredients.

P Kiran is producing the movie under Anandi Art Creations. Geethika has played Abhiram‚Äôs love interest, wherein Sada and Kamal Kamaraju will be seen in vital roles.

The film‚Äôs pre-look generated lots of curiosity on the film. It also gave an impression that Ahimsa will be high on action. Since the film‚Äôs shoot is wrapped up, the team will be kick-starting the promotional activities.

RP Patnaik who provided numerous chartbuster albums has scored music for the film. Teja, Anandi Arts Creations, and RP Patnaik have joined forces again after Nuvvu Nenu to deliver another musical blockbuster.

The movie has cinematography handled by Sameer Reddy, while Kotagiri Venkateswara Rao is the editor. Anil Achugatla has penned dialogues and Supriya is the art director.

The makers will soon announce the release date of the movie.

Cast: Abhiram, Geethika, Rajat Bedi, Sadha, Ravi Kale, Kamal Kamaraju, Manoj Tiger, Kalpalatha, Devi Prasad and others.

snippet.description:
Shaakuntalam Official Trailer - Telugu | Samantha, Dev Mohan | Gunasekhar | Feb 17, 2023 Release

Shaakuntalam Movie also in 3D, Written & Directed by Gunasekhar, Presented by Dil Raju under Sri Venkateswara Creations in collaboration with Gunaa Teamworks, Produced by Neelima Guna.

The massively mounted film Shaakuntalam based on internationally acclaimed Kalidasa‚Äôs Sanskrit play ‚ÄòAbhijnana Shakuntalam‚Äô is all set to release in Hindi, Telugu, Tamil, Malayalam & Kannada.  The story of Shaakuntalam revolves around the epic love story of Shakuntala and King Dushyant from Mahabharata, portrayed by Samantha and Dev Mohan.

The film is helmed by supremely proficient, Director Gunasekhar and marks a whimsical tale of love set in the Kashyapa Kanumalu (Kashmir), the grandeur and splendour of Dushyant‚Äôs Puru Dynasty making the film extremely exceptional.

Here is #VeeraSimhaReddy Movie Review, Rating and public talk. #VeeraSimhaReddy is an Intense Thrilling Mass Action enyertainer. #VeeraSimhaReddy movie story deals with Veera Simha Reddy and His mass swag. #VeeraSimhaReddy Review reveals positives and negatives of the film in detail. 

Natasimha #NandamuriBalakrishna #ShrutiHaasan are the lead actors in #VeeraSimhaReddy movie. Dhuniya Vijay, Honey Rose,Varalakshmi Sharathkumar, Laal, Naveen Chandra and others are the key cast in #VeeraSimhaReddy. Gopichand Malineni directed the film #VeeraSimhaReddy. S S Thaman did music for #VeeraSimhaReddy 2022 movie. Mytri Movie Makers produced the film. Catch complete review of #VeeraSimhaReddy Movie in Telugu in the video.

snippet.description:
Veera Simha Reddy Trailer on Mythri Movie Makers. Presenting our NATASIMHAM Nandamuri Balakrishna, Shruti Haasan and Varalaxmi Sarathkumar in Veera Simha Reddy. About Film Companion South:
Film Companion South is a division of Film Companion, founded by film critic and author Anupama Chopra. Apart from film reviews and articles, Film Companion South, with programs in Tamil, Malayalam, Telugu, and Kannada, specializes in conducting in-depth interviews with film personalities which include the likes of Kamal Hassan, Mani Ratnam, Academy Award-winner AR Rahman, Vetrimaaran, Dhanush, Yash, Sruthi Hariharan, Mahesh Babu, NTR Jr, Samantha, Aishwarya Rajesh, Ramya Krishnan, Prithviraj, Anjali Menon, Mysskin, Gautam Vasudev Menon, Rajamouli, Ram Charan, Yash, Prashanth Neel, Venkat Prabhu, Nelson, Sivakarthikeyan, Rakshit Shetty and many more. The channel has also hosted shows which open up the lesser-known facets of filmmaking with conversations with PC Sreeram, Ravi Varman, Rajiv Menon, Thota Tharani, and Academy Award-winner Resul Pookutty. In other words, Film Companion South is for those who love their cinema and are unapologetic about it.

‚ñ∫*About*
-------------
RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye‚Ä¶ parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!

snippet.title: Crypto Ke Paise || Appurv Gupta aka GuptaJi | Stand Up Comedy | Crowd Work
snippet.description:
Hello Dosto,

Kaise ho aap sab?

Before I upload my content videos, I want to make this channel active so uploading one crowdwork video and then Ill start up content video. In this video, I met a group of freinds who are into various fields and this another person who are making money from crypto investment.

Presenting a crowd work stand up comedy video which we have recorded in November at The Laugh Club, Chandigarh. 

Hope you enjoy this video. 

And Yes, After a wild tour of Kaafi Wild Hai, I am presenting my new show 
GENUINELY which I am touring these days. 
Why Genuinely? Because this time everything from heart so everything is Genuine.

Aao show mien, sab content genuine milega.

If you want to come for the GENUINELY tour, here is the ticket link : https://linktr.ee/appurvgupta

Book Now as we have limited seats in every city.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3665 - 11 Jan 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3665: Bagha Ho Gaya Seedha
--------------------------------------------------------
After a desperate search finally, through Jetha's mobile tracker Gokuldham men finally get to know Bagha's whereabouts. They find him indulging in alcohol while sitting at a bar. They notice that Bagha has already been intoxicated. Bagha gets high under the influence of alcohol and heartbreaking poetry. Finally, the Gokuldham men decide to carry Bagha and bring him into society. Dr. Hathi has some pills to bring Bagha back to his senses. After Bagha's break-up, he seems to have become a little adamant. Will Bagha agree to take the pills? Stay tuned!

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3665, 11 Jan 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sab

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.title: Real Madrid 1-1 Valencia (4-3 penalties) | HIGHLIGHTS | Spanish Super Cup
snippet.description:
Real Madrid have reached the Spanish Super Cup final after defeating Valencia on penalties (4-3) following a 1-1 draw. Karim Benzema opened the scoring with a first-half penalty before Samuel Lino levelled for Valencia shortly after the break. Neither of the two sides found the back of the net after that and forced extra-time and penalties. All four of Carlo Ancelotti's penalty-takers - Karim Benzema, Luka Modriƒá, Toni Kroos and Marco Asensio - netted from 12 yards out, while goalkeeper Thibaut Courtois saved Jos√© Luis Gay√†'s penalty to ensure Real Madrid's place in this weekend's final, where they will face FC Barcelona or Real Betis.

snippet.title: 2nd ODI | Highlights | New Zealand Tour Of Pakistan | 11th January 2023
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony LIV Channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/sonyliv
 
Click here to watch all highlights: https://bit.ly/3V8TM1y

Click here to watch more: https://www.sonyliv.com/sports/cricket-new-zealand-tour-of-pakistan-2022-23-1500003680

Click here to subscribe now: https://bit.ly/3Q78rHU

The 2nd ODI started off with New Zealand coming in to bat first. Devon Conway led the batting with a strong century whereas Kane Willamson made a vital 85 run knock helping New Zealand to reach 261 runs. Pakistan never looked in control as they kept on losing wickets at regular intervals which resulted in Pakistan losing by a big margin of 79 runs.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3664 - 10 Jan 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3664: Bagha Bhaag Gaya
--------------------------------------------------------
All Gokuldham men discuss Bagha's breakup with Bawri, and they also empathize with his situation. Jetha shares his concerns about his delivery of fifty LCD television sets, which seems difficult without Bagha. The Gokuldham ladies also discuss Bagha's melancholy situation and pray for his fast recovery. Later, Nattu Kaka is unable to find Bagha in their apartment, so he rushes to Gokuldham because Jetha's phone can track Bagha's location. After such a painful break-up, in what situation will they find Bagha? Stay tuned!

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3664, 10 Jan 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sab

http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.title: Kya Karoon - Sanam Puri | Jaani | Jasmin Bhasin | Arvindr Khaira | Desi Melodies
snippet.description:
Desi Melodies is kicking off the year with Sanam Puri‚Äôs golden voice combined with Jaani‚Äôs lily-white lyrics and composition in the form of ‚ÄòKya Karoon‚Äô - guaranteed to give you sonic goosebumps.

‚ÄòKya Karoon‚Äô is a heart-wrenching ballad that tells the story of two lovers held together by emotive lyrics and soulful melodies, combined with Puri's smooth that transport the listener to a world of love, longing, and heartache. The music video directed by Arvindr Khaira, is a visual feast, featuring Sanam and Jasmin Bhasin in a raw yet dreamy atmosphere. As the song builds to its emotional climax, it's clear that this is a love that will stand the test of time, unwavering and true.

‚ñ∫*About*
-------------
RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye‚Ä¶ parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!


Jaanne ke liye dekhiye #RadhaKrishn, Somvaar se Shanivaar, shaam 7.30 baje, sirf #StarBharat par. Krishn aur Radha ki leelaon se judde rehne ke liye hamein follow kariye Instagram, Facebook aur YouTube par!
